{
  "stem": "2804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we knew we going-- we weren't going to the CBI or the China-Burma area or-- we were headed for the ETO, Theater of Operations, that European Theater.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was about the same age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 23 at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few of them were a little bit older, maybe 28.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them were 30.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the only Jewish nurse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never had any problems, or-- because the majority of the doctors and the GIs came from the New York area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had quite a few came from Brooklyn, from the Bronx, Long Island.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had also some doctors coming from the other end, from California and the Midwest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were-- at that time, I felt-- and even my husband, his father at the time had said, this is-- it's like a Jewish war, and all the Jewish boys should join, should sign up and fight for their rights.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not that aware.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the answer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I fault our government, very much so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were the lead ship going over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went over with the-- I think it was the 17th Armored Division from Texas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had three or four other ships in our convoy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we hit the English Channel, we did not get to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went in-- we landed at Le Havre.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the night before, or two days before, I remember suddenly they spotted some submarines, and they started to drop the depth charges.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very scary.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not only that, but I didn't know how to swim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I held onto my life belt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I-- I did not leave it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
